{"tid":831062,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［電腦求救］大神麻煩入入黎","createTime":"2018-09-21T15:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T04:37:39.000Z","uid":114427,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"95e35de4c91bfa695150871b7a42463553675c4c","tid":831062,"uid":114427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱更新左mb bios 好似失敗左？！<br />\n呢家情況係咁<br />\n1.入到bios setting (入面睇就係更新完果個bios ver.)<br />\n2.唔入bios就無限reboot<br />\n<br />\n嘗試過既自救方法<br />\n1.用win10手指boot部機 <br />\n結果 reboot again<br />\n2.用舊bios overwrite <br />\n結果 提示更新失敗<br />\n3.重插ram<br />\n結果 reboot again<br />\n4.bios default setting<br />\n結果 reboot<br />\n5.鬆左火牛去display既線（供電線？！）<br />\n結果 無reboot 不過無onboard display 所以唔知究竟係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無大神可以提供其他方法（換硬件除外）嘗試自救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c36e425868b81bccd75af189b9464231726708","tid":831062,"uid":114427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}